The lawmaker has been advocating for U.S. President Donald Trump to attack [Iran](https://www.foxnews.com/category/world/conflicts/iran).

"President Trump's resolve is not the question: Question is, when we do an operation like this, should it be bigger, or smaller? I'm in the camp of bigger," Graham [said](https://x.com/LindseyGrahamSC/status/2011839849611825589) in footage he highlighted in a Thursday [post](https://x.com/LindseyGrahamSC/status/2011839849611825589) on X. "Time will tell. I'm hopeful and optimistic that the regime days are numbered."

